<b>It's me!</b>

14:38.831 --> 14:39.881
<b>Stop...</b>

14:48.131 --> 14:51.551
<b>Special Attack: Hammer Shooting Star!!</b>

15:01.901 --> 15:03.521
<b>Veau Vengeance!!</b>

15:03.521 --> 15:05.991
<b>Swan Bombardier Dive!!</b>

15:32.551 --> 15:34.061
<b>Take this...</b>

15:34.061 --> 15:36.471
<b>Tornado Tempo!</b>

15:48.151 --> 15:49.281
<b>What?!</b>

15:59.001 --> 16:04.041
<b>One-Sword Style Iai Draw and 
