<b>Let me tell you something...</b>

16:21.441 --> 16:24.941
<b>You can't save this country.</b>

16:27.401 --> 16:30.611
<b>Goodbye, Princess...</b>

16:37.331 --> 16:40.161
<b>Crocodile!!</b>

16:42.041 --> 16:43.421
<b>Luffy-<i>san</i>!</b>

16:52.931 --> 16:54.141
<b>Just in time.</b>

17:01.021 --> 17:02.291
<b>Vivi...</b>

17:02.291 --> 17:05.001
<b>She tells others not to die...</b>

17:05.001 --> 17:09.151
<b>but she's the first to lay down her own life
to save others.</b>

17:09.821 --> 17:12.111
<b>If we don't help her, she'll die.</b>

17:12.611 --> 17:14.531
<b>You guys will kill her.</b>

17:14.791 --> 17:17.281
<b>You're so dense.</b>

17:17.281 --> 17:21.001
<b>That's why I'm telling you
that you can just ditch that burden...!</b>

17:21.791 --> 17:25.711
<b>We don't want her to die!
That's how friends are!</b>

17:31.211 --> 17:34.011
<b>Please... stop fighting!</b>

17:34.011 --> 17:37.351
<b>Please... stop fighting!</b>

17:37.351 --> 17:41.221
<b>Please... stop fighting!</b>

17:42.481 --> 17:46.401
<b>Who the hell do you think I am?!</b>

17:46.981 --> 17:49.151
<b>I don't care who you are...</b>

17:49.151 --> 17:51.901
<b>I'll surpass you!</b>

17:57.321 --> 17:59.571
<b>Gum-Gum...!</b>

17:59.571 --> 18:01.291
<b>Desert...</b>

18:01.291 --> 18:03.201
<b>Storm!</b>

18:03.201 --> 18:05.501
<b>La Spada!</b>

18:35.701 --> 18:37.491
<b>Luffy-<i>san</i>...</b>

18:40.321 --> 18:44.301
<b>Please stop fighting!</b>

18:45.791 --> 18:50.701
<b>Please don't fight... any more...!!</b>

18:54.961 --> 18:58.941
<b>Since our nightmares are... all over...</b>

19:00.091 --> 19:03.751
<b><i><i>Crocodile's plot was thwarted 
by Luffy and the others and</i></i></b>

19:03.751 --> 19:06.001
<b><i>the Alabasta Kingdom was saved.</i></b>

19:06.341 --> 19:09.871
<b><i>However, the Straw Hats 
didn't get credit for it,</i></b>

19:09.871 --> 19:13.521
<b><i>because the Government reported that
it was the Navy's achievement.</i></b>

19:15.651 --> 19:17.201
<b>Say, everyone...</b>

19:17.611 --> 19:20.201
<b>What... should I do...?</b>

19:22.161 --> 19:27.331
<b>We'll draw the ship near the eastern harbor
just once at exactly noon tomorrow.</b>

19:28.001 --> 19:31.281
<b>If you want to continue traveling with us,
that moment is the</b>

19:31.281 --> 19:33.801
<b>only chance to come aboard.</b>

19:34.131 --> 19:37.761
<b>If that happens, we'll welcome you...
though you'll become a pirate.</b>

19:37.761 --> 19:41.391
<b>Come, Vivi! Definitely come! Come now!</b>

19:42.261 --> 19:45.971
<b>If I go, you'll go too, right?</b>

19:46.641 --> 19:48.351
<b>Say... Karoo...</b>

19:49.201 --> 19:50.561
<b>What would <i>you</i> like to do?</b>

19:55.691 --> 19:57.421
<b>Everyone!</b>

19:58.741 --> 19:59.821
<b>Vivi!</b>

19:59.821 --> 20:01.331
<b>Karoo!</b>

20:01.331 --> 20:02.621
<b>Vivi-<i>chan</i>!</b>

20:02.621 --> 20:04.911
<b>Let's go back! Better hurry!</b>

20:04.911 --> 20:07.121
<b>The Navy is right there, too!</b>

20:09.541 --> 20:12.581
<b>I came to say goodbye!</b>

20:13.671 --> 20:15.171
<b>What did she just...?</b>

20:16.751 --> 20:19.971
<b>I can't... go with you!</b>

20:19.971 --> 20:22.601
<b><i>Thank you so much for everything!</i></b>

20:23.891 --> 20:25.911
<b>I'd like to go on more adventures,</b>

20:25.911 --> 20:30.881
<b>but there's no ignoring... 
that I love this country!</b>

20:31.561 --> 20:34.011
<b><i>So I can't go!</i></b>

20:35.311 --> 20:36.361
<b>I see!</b>

20:36.821 --> 20:38.151
<b><i>I...</i></b>

20:38.611 --> 20:40.031
<b><i>I...</i></b>

20:40.491 --> 20:42.071
<b>I...</b>

20:44.531 --> 20:46.851
<b>If we ever meet again someday...</b>

20:46.851 --> 20:50.501
<b>will you call me your friend again?!</b>

21:07.761 --> 21:13.691
<b><i>All right! At any rate, no matter what happens,
this thing on our left arm...</i></b>

21:14.651 --> 21:16.681
<b><i>...is the sign of our friendship!</i></b>

21:18.111 --> 21:21.111
<b>They don't like to be seen as heroes...</b>

21:21.491 --> 21:26.431
<b>And because of their bounties and people's talk,
they keep gaining notoriety,</b>

21:26.431 --> 21:29.461
<b>but I'm sure they haven't changed.</b>

21:29.831 --> 21:33.041
<b>When I read about Dressrosa,</b>

21:33.041 --> 21:38.001
<b>I knew that Luffy-<i>san</i> and the others decided to
save somebody again!</b>

21:39.291 --> 21:41.551
<b>That's right!</b>

21:42.801 --> 21:44.881
<b>To us, Luffy is...</b>

21:44.881 --> 21:49.181
<b>The Straw Hats are very special!</b>

21:54.021 --> 21:56.311
<b>I miss him... Lucy...</b>

21:58.311 --> 22:00.021
<b>Um...</b>

22:00.651 --> 22:04.991
<b>Were you talking about Luffy-<i>sama</i> just now?</b>

22:04.991 --> 22:06.951
<b>Oh, the Mermaid Princess!</b>

22:07.991 --> 22:09.281
<b>Shirahoshi!</b>

22:10.121 --> 22:12.721
<b>Talking about him doesn't always mean
they know him!</b>

22:12.721 --> 22:17.331
<b>Luffy-<i>kun</i> is a pirate!
If someone finds out you're his friend-<i>ti-do</i>!</b>

22:19.001 --> 22:21.301
<b><i>The Mermaid Princess knows Luffy-</i>san<i>?</i></b>

22:21.301 --> 22:24.011
<b>Hey, did you just say Luffy-<i>sama</i>?</b>

22:24.011 --> 22:26.971
<b>Wait, Rebecca! If we heard wrong...</b>

22:26.971 --> 22:27.641
<b>Yes!</b>

22:27.641 --> 22:30.601
<b>I did say so! Do you know him?!</b>

22:30.601 --> 22:33.311
<b>Stop! Everyone knows his name!</b>

22:33.311 --> 22:37.061
<b>I'm indebted to Luffy-<i>sama</i>...</b>

22:40.151 --> 22:41.191
<b>So are we!</b>

22:44.611 --> 22:47.911
<b>Your voice is heard by us.</b>

22:50.531 --> 22:51.821
<b>Let's go for a walk!</b>

22:55.371 --> 22:58.921
<b>I bet you're happy, Rebecca,
to see your dad!</b>

23:09.891 --> 23:13.811
<b><i>In front of Vivi and the others,
the Sakura Kingdom's Dalton, Dr. Kureha,</i></b>

23:13.811 --> 23:18.561
<b><i>and their arch-enemy Wapol appear
and tensions rise in the Holyland!</i></b>

23:18.561 --> 23:22.651
<b><i><i>Meanwhile, a lone figure goes deep inside
the Pangaea Castle</i></i></b>

23:22.651 --> 23:25.861
<b><i>and a great hidden secret is unveiled!</i></b>

23:25.861 --> 23:27.331
<b>On the next episode of One Piece!</b>

23:27.331 --> 23:30.651
<b>"In the Dark Recesses of the Holyland! 
